Class BindingBuilder<T extends InjectorBuilder<T>>

java.lang.Object
honeyroasted.fill.bindings.BindingBuilder<T>
public class BindingBuilder<T extends InjectorBuilder<T>> extends Object
An intermediate builder that takes a Matcher and ReflectionInjectorBuilder and constructs a Binding and adds it to the ReflectionInjectorBuilder
